      "updated": 1765907906584,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "turnaround(FIM - CHEGADA)\nP0 0.4 - 0.0 = 0.4 -->processo\nP1  0.1 - 0.0 = 0.1\nP2 0.2 - 0.1 = 0.1\nP3 1.4 - 0.1 = 1.3\nP4 0.7 - 0.5 = 0.2\nP5 1.0 - 0.5 = 0.5\n\nturnaround MEDIO : soma dos processos/n de processos\n0.4+0.1+0.1+1.3+0.2+0.5=2.6\n2.6/6 = 0.433 \n\ntempo de espera (turnaround - Duração)\nP0 0.4 - 0.2 = 0.2 -->processo\nP1  0.1 - 0.1 = 0.0\nP2 0.1 - 0.1 = 0.0\nP3 1.3 - 0.5 = 0.8\nP4 0.2 - 0.2 = 0.0\nP5 0.5 - 0.3 = 0.2\n\ntempo de espera MEDIO: soma dos tempos /n de processos\n0.2+0.0+0.0+0.8+0.0+0.2=1.2\n1.2/6=0.2\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "turnaround(FIM - CHEGADA)\nP0 0.4 - 0.0 = 0.4 -->processo\nP1  0.1 - 0.0 = 0.1\nP2 0.2 - 0.1 = 0.1\nP3 1.4 - 0.1 = 1.3\nP4 0.7 - 0.5 = 0.2\nP5 1.0 - 0.5 = 0.5\n\nturnaround MEDIO : soma dos processos/n de processos\n0.4+0.1+0.1+1.3+0.2+0.5=2.6\n2.6/6 = 0.433 \n\ntempo de espera (turnaround - Duração)\nP0 0.4 - 0.2 = 0.2 -->processo\nP1  0.1 - 0.1 = 0.0\nP2 0.1 - 0.1 = 0.0\nP3 1.3 - 0.5 = 0.8\nP4 0.2 - 0.2 = 0.0\nP5 0.5 - 0.3 = 0.2\n\ntempo de espera MEDIO: soma dos tempos /n de processos\n0.2+0.0+0.0+0.8+0.0+0.2=1.2\n1.2/6=0.2\n",
