      "updated": 1765921488221,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TURNAROUND RR(FIM - CHEGADA)\nPO 0.2 - 0.0 = 0.2 -->processo\nP1  0.3 - 0.0=0.3\nP2 0.4 - 0.1=0.3\nP3  0.9 - 0.1=0.8\nP4  1.1 - 0.5=0.6\nP5  1.4 - 0.5=0.9\n\nturnaround RR MEDIO : soma dos processos/n de processos\n0.2+0.3+0.3+0.8+0.6+0.9=2.9\n2.6/6 = 0.483 \n\ntempo de espera RR (turnaround - Duração)\nP0 0.2 - 0.2 = 0.0 -->processo\nP1 0.3 -0.1= 0.2\nP2 0.3 -0.1= 0.2\nP3 0.8 -0.5=0.3\nP4 0.6 -0.2=0.4\nP5 0.9 -0.3=0.6\n\ntempo de espera RR MEDIO: soma dos tempos /n de processos\n0.2+0.2+0.3+0.4+0.6+0.0=1.7\n1.7/6=2.83\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TURNAROUND RR(FIM - CHEGADA)\nPO 0.2 - 0.0 = 0.2 -->processo\nP1  0.3 - 0.0=0.3\nP2 0.4 - 0.1=0.3\nP3  0.9 - 0.1=0.8\nP4  1.1 - 0.5=0.6\nP5  1.4 - 0.5=0.9\n\nturnaround RR MEDIO : soma dos processos/n de processos\n0.2+0.3+0.3+0.8+0.6+0.9=2.9\n2.6/6 = 0.483 \n\ntempo de espera RR (turnaround - Duração)\nP0 0.2 - 0.2 = 0.0 -->processo\nP1 0.3 -0.1= 0.2\nP2 0.3 -0.1= 0.2\nP3 0.8 -0.5=0.3\nP4 0.6 -0.2=0.4\nP5 0.9 -0.3=0.6\n\ntempo de espera RR MEDIO: soma dos tempos /n de processos\n0.2+0.2+0.3+0.4+0.6+0.0=1.7\n1.7/6=2.83\n",
